<?php
return ['messages'=>['#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/'=>'#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/','<h3 class="post_title entry-title"><a href="https://eji.com.hk/behind-the-scenes-ensuring-responsible-jewellery-quality-and-value-2/">BEHIND THE SCENES: ENSURING RESPONSIBLE JEWELLERY QUALITY AND VALUE</a></h3>'=>'<h3 class="post_title entry-title"><a href="https://eji.com.hk/zh-hans/%e5%b9%95%e5%90%8e%e8%8a%b1%e7%b5%ae%e7%a1%ae%e4%bf%9d%e8%b4%9f%e8%b4%a3%e4%bb%bb%e7%9a%84%e7%8f%a0%e5%ae%9d%e8%b4%a8%e9%87%8f%e5%92%8c%e4%bb%b7%e5%80%bc/">幕后：确保负责任的珠宝质量和价值</a></h3>','<h5>May 30, Friday - June 2, Sunday<br />9:30am - 6:00pm</h5><h5>June 3, Monday<br />9:30am - 4:00pm</h5>'=>'<h5>5 月 30 日星期五至 6 月 2 日星期日<br>上午 9:30 - 下午 6:00</h5><h5>6 月 3 日星期一<br>上午 9:30 - 下午 4:00</h5>','<p>After the final touches, every piece undergoes a strict quality control process to guarantee it is free of defects and meets our high standards of craftsmanship. This ensures that each piece we craft carries the hallmark of unparalleled quality and an enduring commitment to excellence.</p>'=>'<p>在最后的润色之后，每一件作品都要经过严格的质量控制流程，以确保其无瑕疵，并符合我们的高工艺标准。这确保了我们的每一件作品都具有无与伦比的品质和追求卓越的恒久承诺。 </p>','<p>At EJI, we are more than just a qualified fine jewellery manufacturer, we are artisans dedicated to the craft of fine jewellery creation. Each piece we create is a testament to our commitment to excellence. Join us as we take you behind the scenes of our intricate manufacturing steps, ensuring every detail is nothing short of perfect.</p>'=>'<p>在 EJI，我们不仅仅是一家合格的高级珠宝制造商，我们还是致力于高级珠宝制作工艺的工匠。我们的每一件作品都是我们追求卓越承诺的见证。让我们带您了解我们复杂的生产步骤，确保每一个细节都尽善尽美。  </p>','<p>Diamond setting is an art form in itself. Our most experienced jewellers delicately secure each diamond, optimizing the stone’s visibility and brilliance while ensuring it is held firmly. The beauty of the jewellery hinges on the perfection of its setting.</p>'=>'<p>钻石镶嵌本身就是一门艺术。我们最有经验的珠宝匠会细心地固定每一颗钻石，在确保钻石稳固的同时，优化钻石的可见度和亮度。珠宝的美丽取决于镶嵌的完美。  </p>','<p>Equipped with the most advanced technology equipment, we combine exceptional expertise and meticulous craftsmanship in our creations. The entire process is well-established to foster precision and maintain the highest standards. Our commitment extends beyond the creation of fine jewellery; we endeavour to deliver exceptional service that exceeds your expectations, from the initial design concept to the final creation.</p>'=>'<p>我们配备了最先进的技术设备，将非凡的专业知识和一丝不苟的工艺完美地结合在一起。整个工艺流程都经过精心设计，以提高精确度并保持最高标准。我们的承诺不仅仅局限于制作精美的珠宝，从最初的设计理念到最终的作品，我们都致力于提供超越您期望的卓越服务。  </p>','<p>Every exquisite jewellery creation begins with an idea – a vision born from the concept to embark on this production journey. Our skilled designers are artists who transform inspiration to design sketches, capturing classic elegance alongside innovation trends.</p>'=>'<p>每一件精美绝伦的珠宝作品都始于一个想法--一个从概念中诞生的愿景，开启了这一生产之旅。我们技艺精湛的设计师都是艺术家，他们将灵感转化为设计草图，在创新潮流中捕捉经典优雅。 </p>','<p>Following the CAD process, we utilize 3D printer to create a precise physical model of the design. This pivotal step not only confirms the design’s feasibility but also allows for any necessary adjustments, greatly enhancing our capabilities in handling big orders with precision and efficiency.</p><p>Through our sophisticated casting process, the model is transformed into precious metal. As it cools and hardens, it adopts the shape form of the mould, ready for further refinement and assembly.</p>'=>'<p>在 CAD 流程之后，我们利用 3D 打印机创建设计的精确实体模型。这一关键步骤不仅确认了设计的可行性，还允许进行任何必要的调整，从而大大提高了我们精准高效地处理大订单的能力。 </p><p>通过我们精密的铸造工艺，模型被转化为贵金属。在冷却和硬化过程中，它将采用模具的形状，以便进一步完善和组装。 </p>','<p>Polishing is the penultimate step that brings out the vibrant shine and smooth finish of our jewellery. Following that, rhodium plating enhances the shine further while significantly increasing the durability and resistance to scratches and tarnish. This ensures each piece not only looks spectacular but is also crafted to last a lifetime.</p>'=>'<p>抛光是倒数第二道工序，它能使我们的首饰呈现出鲜艳的光泽和光滑的表面。之后，镀铑进一步增强了光泽，同时大大提高了耐用性和抗划痕和玷污能力。这就确保了每件饰品不仅美观大方，而且经久耐用。  </p>','<p>Post-casting, each piece of casting undergoes a rigorous grinding process to remove rough edges and smoothen the surface. Grinding is a crucial step in our manufacturing process, requiring highly precise skills and a great deal of attention to detail. This ensures that the pieces are in their final form and free from imperfections.</p><p>Following this, the jewellery pieces are assembled with absolute precision. Our skilled jewellers ensure that each component fits flawlessly, setting the stage for the brilliance of diamonds to come.</p>'=>'<p>铸造后，每件铸件都要经过严格的打磨工序，以去除粗糙的边缘，使表面更加光滑。打磨是我们制造过程中的关键步骤，需要高度精确的技术和对细节的关注。这确保了铸件的最终形态，没有任何瑕疵。  </p><p>之后，珠宝首饰将以绝对精确的方式组装起来。我们技艺精湛的珠宝匠确保每个部件都完美无瑕，为钻石的璀璨夺目奠定基础。 </p>','<p>Whether you’re launching a new jewellery business, or you’re a savvy chain store owner looking for wholesale opportunities, we invite you to discover our breathtaking fine jewellery collections and learn more about our personalized services at the upcoming <a href="https://jck24.nvytes.co/jck24/landing/CIP104.html">JCK Las Vegas 2024</a>. We’re ready to showcase a potent blend of excellence and elegance. See ya there!</p>'=>'<p>无论您是正在开展新的珠宝业务，还是正在寻找批发机会的精明连锁店主，我们都诚邀您在即将到来的<a href="https://jck24.nvytes.co/jck24/landing/CIP104.html">JCK Las Vegas 2024</a> 展会上一睹我们令人叹为观止的高级珠宝系列，并进一步了解我们的个性化服务。我们已准备好展示卓越与优雅的完美融合。到时见！  </p>','<p>With the initial design in hand, we move to the Computer-Aided Design (CAD) stage. Here, our CAD specialists create a 3D model from sketch, visualizing the final product and allowing us to refine every facet of the jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>有了初步设计，我们就进入计算机辅助设计（CAD）阶段。在这里，我们的 CAD 专家根据草图创建三维模型，将最终产品形象化，使我们能够完善珠宝的方方面面。 </p>','Advanced Technology Meets Precision: The CAD Stage'=>'先进技术与高精度的完美结合：CAD 阶段','Bringing Designs to Life: 3D Printing and Casting'=>'让设计栩栩如生：3D 打印和铸造','Contact Our Sales Experts'=>'联系我们的销售专家','Continue Reading'=>'继续阅读','Final Touches: Polishing and Rhodium Plating'=